source: (BALLORA)\\\\I can hear someone creeping through my room.
target: (芭萝菈)\\\\我能听到有人在我的房间里悄悄地走动。

source: (BALLORA)\\\\Why do you hide inside the walls, when there is music in my halls? All I see is an\\empty room. No more joy, like an empty tomb. It's so good to sing all day. To dance, \\to spin, to fly away.
target: (芭萝菈)\\\\当我的大厅里有音乐时，你为什么要躲在墙壁里？我看到的只是一个\\空荡荡的房间。没有了欢乐，就像一个空荡荡的坟墓。整天唱歌是多么美好。跳舞，\\旋转，飞翔。
(比迪巴)\\\\我们很快会再来见你。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\"Come." The boy said. "Rest here before killing the witch."
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\“来吧。”男孩说。“在杀死女巫之前在这里休息一下。”

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\....It was a limited time offer that included a family style pizza with all their\\favorite toppings.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\....这是一份限时供应，包括了一份家庭风格的披萨，上面有他们\\最喜欢的小料。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\Come get your candy here. Candy. Candy. Can.. can... candy.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\来这里拿你的糖果吧。糖果。糖果。糖..糖...糖果。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\Now I will tell you a story...
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\现在我要给你讲一个故事...

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\Now let me tell you a story about a young woman who, when she was little, was led into\\a dark forest by a witch, and almost eaten.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\现在让我给你讲一个关于一个年轻女人的故事，她小时候被一个女巫带进\\了一个黑暗的森林，差点被吃掉。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\She followed the boy into the house.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\她跟着男孩走进了房子。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\She had escaped before being thrown into the oven, but would have a scar for the\\rest of her life.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\她在被扔进烤箱之前逃脱了，但她的身上会留下一个\\终生的疤痕。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\She had fallen for the friendly voice without discernment, and was led astray.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\她听信了那友好的声音而没有辨别力，因而误入歧途。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\She was greeted at the mouth of the forest by a young boy who offered to help guide\\her through the darkness.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\她在森林的入口处遇到了一个年轻的男孩，他主动提出要帮助她\\穿过黑暗。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\She welcomed the help, and followed the young boy over the river, through the jagged trees,\\and toward a small house.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\她高兴的接受了他的帮助，跟着年轻的男孩过了河，穿过了密集的树林，\\朝着一座小房子走去。
(糖果机器人)\\\\烤箱的门关上了。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\The witch would finally have her meal.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\女巫终于要大快朵颐了。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\The young woman was tired, and would kill the witch in the morning.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\年轻的女人很累，她打算第二天再杀死女巫。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\When she had grown, she sought revenge on the witch, and entered the forest again\\willingly, this time with the confidence of age and experience.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\当她长大后，她寻求对女巫的复仇，又一次自愿地进入了森林\\这一次，她有了年龄和经验的自信。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\…About a family that missed the most important opportunity in their lives.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\...关于一个错过了他们生命中最重要的机会的家庭的故事。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\…It also came with a side of fries, mozzarella sticks, extra large\\soft drinks and a toy surprise..
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\...它还附带了薯条、马苏里拉奶酪条、超大杯无酒精饮料和一个玩具惊喜...

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\…It was only $49.99 while supplies lasted.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\...只要货源充足，它只要49.99美元。

source: (CANDY CADET)\\\\…They did not purchase the food and they all died.
target: (糖果机器人)\\\\...他们没有购买食物，他们都死了。

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\Aim to get the high score or I'll give ye the ol cactus keel haul!
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\争取得到最高分，否则我就让你尝尝仙人掌的滋味！

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\And the real treasure was booty all along.
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\原来真正的宝藏一直都是战利品。

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\And the real treasure was friendship all along.
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\原来真正的宝藏一直都是友谊。

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\Argh, let’s see how ye did.
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\啊，让我们看看你的表现。

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\Have a rootin' tootin' time. Yee Harr!!
(CAPT. FOXY)\\\\It be recommended that ye stay on the approved route.
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\建议你沿着指定的路线走。

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\Keep yer hands and feet in the ride at all times, or ye’ll end up like me!
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\时刻保持你的手和脚在游乐设施内，否则你会变成我这样！

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\There’s gold in them thar hills!
(CAPT. FOXY)\\\\This here’s a robbery! Make with the loot!
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\这是一场抢劫！快交出财物！

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\Use them there hand cannons to shoot anything that moves!
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\用那些手炮射击任何动的东西！

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\We be not responsible for any maimings or mayhem that might happen on this here path.
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\我们不对这条路上可能发生的任何伤残事故或混乱负责。

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\We be not responsible for any maimings that might happen on this here path.
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\我们不对这条路上可能发生的任何伤残事故负责。

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\Welcome to CAPTAIN FOXY'S COWBOY ADVENTURE.
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\欢迎来到霍斯船长的牛仔冒险。

source: (CAPT. FOXY)\\\\Yo ho ho and a bottle of Fizzy Faz!
target: (霍斯船长)\\\\呦吼吼，一瓶费斯汽水！
(卡尼)\\\\又一个赢家？去拿你的奖品吧。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Awww… I almost feel sorry for ya. Just to be clear, I don’t.
target: (卡尼)\\\\哎呀...我差点为你感到难过。不过我要澄清一下，只是差点难过。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Back again to test yer skill. Well, here’s another one from the vaults!
target: (卡尼)\\\\又回来测试你的技能了。好吧，这里有另一个从保险库里拿出来的！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Back again? Well, I am sure we can find something a little more difficult to test yer\\troubling talents. Fish on!
target: (卡尼)\\\\又回来了？好吧，我敢肯定我们可以找到一些更难的东西来考验你的\\令人头疼的才能。加油吧！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Back for more? Truly a glutton fer punishment.
target: (卡尼)\\\\又来了？你是不是有啥受虐倾向？

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Can’t knock that one over with a zap gun!
target: (卡尼)\\\\你用那个电击枪是打不倒那个的！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Come on. The ball is in the basket. Are ya unfamiliar with the concept of ball toss?
target: (卡尼)\\\\快点。球在篮子里。你不懂扔球的概念吗？
(卡尼)\\\\你喜欢飞镖，高科技激光吗？

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Don’t take a genius to know that won’t work.
target: (卡尼)\\\\不用是天才就知道那不会有效果。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Ever dream of shootin’ a real life sci-fi laser?
target: (卡尼)\\\\你有没有梦想过用一把真正的科幻激光枪射击？
(卡尼)\\\\Faz激光枪有你想要的一切！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Gather round folks! Come see the worst Fazerblast player in the history of Fall Fest!
target: (卡尼)\\\\大家围过来！来看看秋季节庆史上最糟糕的激光枪玩家！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Get a load of this one folks, thinks that dart can trigger a light sensor. What a maroon!
target: (卡尼)\\\\大家看看这个，以为飞镖能触发光敏传感器。真是个傻瓜！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Get me some popcorn. I’m lovin’ this.
target: (卡尼)\\\\给我弄点爆米花。我爱死这个了。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Gonna need something bigger if you want to knock down that target!
target: (卡尼)\\\\如果你想打倒那个目标，你得用更大的东西！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Had a feelin’ I’d be seeing your ugly mug again.
target: (卡尼)\\\\我就知道我会再见到你的丑脸。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Hey sharpshooter. I got you a little gift.
target: (卡尼)\\\\嘿，神枪手。我给你准备了个小礼物。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\How about we try something a little bit more challenging?
target: (卡尼)\\\\我们试试更有挑战性的怎么样？

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Just pick up a ball and toss it.
target: (卡尼)\\\\只要拿起一个球，然后扔出去。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Just pick up that dart gun and get to shootin’.
target: (卡尼)\\\\只要拿起那把飞镖枪，然后开始射击。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Just shoot the button and take a chance.
target: (卡尼)\\\\只要射中那个按钮，就有机会。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Just shoot the targets and take a chance.
target: (卡尼)\\\\只要射中那些目标，就有机会。
(卡尼)\\\\激光是射不破气球的！哈哈哈。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Look. This is the last time. There’s nothin’ left!
target: (卡尼)\\\\听着。这是最后一次了。再也没有机会了！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Looks like we have ourselves a contender!
target: (卡尼)\\\\看起来我们有了一个有实力的对手！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\My biscuits are burnin’! My biscuits are burnin’!
target: (卡尼)\\\\我的饼干烤糊了！我的饼干粘锅了！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Next time bring the whole family for a once in a lifetime unforgettable experience.
target: (卡尼)\\\\下次带上全家人，享受一次千载难逢的难忘体验。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\No hand holding round here.\\\\Learn by doin’. That's what I always say!
target: (卡尼)\\\\这里不需要手把手教。\\\\自己动手，丰衣足食。这就是我一直说的！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Now, you look like you got kids. Win a prize for the little one!
target: (卡尼)\\\\现在，你看起来有孩子了。为小家伙赢得奖品!

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Poppin’ balloons with a throwin’ ball? Now this I gotta see.
target: (卡尼)\\\\扔球砸破气球？这个我得看看。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Score high or face the consequences. That’s the deal.
target: (卡尼)\\\\得高分或者面对后果。这就是规矩。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Step right up. Step right up. Test yer skills an’ win a prize!
target: (卡尼)\\\\快来吧。快来吧。看看自己几斤几两，赢走奖品！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\That light sensor’s fer lazers, not throwin’ balls!
target: (卡尼)\\\\那个光敏传感器是给激光用的，不是给球的！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\The rules should be simple enough for you to understand.
target: (卡尼)\\\\规则应该很简单，你能理解的。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Then you've come to the right place!
(CARNIE)\\\\What’s yer name? Cat got yer tongue? No need to answer. Don’t matter an I don’t care.
target: (卡尼)\\\\你叫什么名字？猫抓了你的舌头？不用回答。无关紧要，我也不在乎。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Whoah! Hold on! I’m on fire! I’m on fire!
target: (卡尼)\\\\哇！等等！我着火了！我着火了！

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Whoah! Watch where yer pointin’ those things.
target: (卡尼)\\\\哇！小心点，注意你的枪口指向。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\Wow. This is gonna be tough fer you, ain’t it?
target: (卡尼)\\\\哇。这对你来说会很难，不是吗？

source: (CARNIE)\\\\You got all the time in the world. I ain't’ goin’ nowhere.
target: (卡尼)\\\\你有的是时间。我不会走的。

source: (CARNIE)\\\\You gotta hit the targets, not avoid them.
target: (卡尼)\\\\你得打中目标，而不是避开它们。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\Adequate work. You have received your Fazbear First Aid certification. You are now\\qualified to administer medical support in all Fazbear Entertainment franchises.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\还算合格。你已经获得了费斯熊急救证书。你现在有资格在所有费斯娱乐连锁店提供医疗支持。
(癫佬护士)\\\\游戏机相关的伤害。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\Avoid undue patient stress. According to comment cards, Patient outbursts bother\\Pizza Place guests.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\避免给病人造成过度的压力。根据评论卡，病人的爆发会对\\披萨店的客人造成困扰。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\Be advised. Prolonged cries may also attract the attention of free\\roaming characters.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\请注意。持续的哭声也可能吸引自由\\漫游的角色的注意。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\But, hey. There is always next time.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\不过，嘿。总有下次的机会。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\Fazbear Entertainment believes in the "sink or swim" training method.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\费斯娱乐相信“不进则退”的培训方法。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\Great news. Due to today’s successful salvage, Pizza Place entertainment value has\\considerably increased. Be warned, Liability Risk has also increased.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\好消息。由于今天的成功回收，披萨店的娱乐价值有了\\显著的提高。但是要注意，责任风险也增加了。

target: (癫佬护士)\\\\好消息。由于今天的成功回收，披萨店的娱乐...\\(剩余的信息无法辨认)

target: (癫佬护士)\\\\好消息。由于今天的成功回收，披萨店的娱乐价值有了提高。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\It is advised that you use only the designated medical instruments relating\\to the current procedure.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\建议你只使用与当前手术相关的指定的医疗器械。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\Now, give the patient a candy.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\现在，给病人一颗糖果。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\Patient lost. In this unlikely event, it is Fazbear Entertainment policy to disavow\\any knowledge of said emergency and blame the parents.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\病人丢失。在这种不太可能发生的情况下，费斯熊娱乐公司的政策是否\\对上述紧急情况有任何了解，并指责家长。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\The operation was a success. Yay.
(CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\The state of the art Fazbear First Aid station comes equipped with the finest life\\saving tools.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\最先进的费斯熊急救站配备了最好的救生工具。
(癫佬护士)\\\\这颗糖果具有法律约束力。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\This training session simulates actual emergency situations you will encounter on a\\day to day basis.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\这个培训课程模拟了你在\\日常工作中会遇到的真实的紧急情况。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\To calm a patient. Apply the relaxation mask until the outburst is under control.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\为了安抚病人。请使用放松面具，直到情绪得到控制。

source: (CARNIVAL NURSE)\\\\Welcome back. The patient is prepped and ready.
target: (癫佬护士)\\\\欢迎回来。病人已经准备好了。

target: (癫佬护士)\\\\你现在有资格在所有\\费斯娱乐连锁店提供医疗支持。

target: (癫佬护士)\\\\你的目标很简单：救治病人，避免诉讼，给病人一颗糖果。

target: (太阳)\\\\无论你做什么，保持灯光开启。

target: (太阳)\\\\当你做完了，按下按钮，让我评估你的作品。

source: (SUN)\\\\You can make crafts, but then you need to go.
target: (太阳)\\\\你可以做手工，但是然后你就要走了。

target: (太阳)\\\\你要呆在禁闭室，直到你的父母来接你。

target: (太阳)\\\\你在黑暗中工作会伤害你的眼睛。

target: (录像带)\\\\费斯熊娱乐承认过去的工作条件并不理想。但是，我们可以为你提供百分之百的“安全意图”保证。（安全不保证）

source: (VIDEO TAPE)\\\\Fazbear Entertainment is offering a new on-the-job training position for a future pizza professional.
target: (录像带)\\\\费斯熊娱乐正在提供一个新的在职培训职位，为未来的披萨专家。

source: (VIDEO TAPE)\\\\To accept this position, press or say “1”.
target: (录像带)\\\\要接受这个职位，请按或说“1”。

source: (VIDEO TAPE)\\\\We didn’t quite get that, but we know what you intended.
target: (录像带)\\\\我们没有听清楚，但是我们知道你的意思。

source: (VOICE)\\\\Don't worry. They can't hear me. I am on a special signal the S.T.A.F.F. can't process.
target: (声音)\\\\别担心。他们听不到我。我在一个特殊的信号上，S.T.A.F.F. 无法处理。

source: (VOICE)\\\\Find a place where we can talk safely.
target: (声音)\\\\找一个我们可以安全交谈的地方。

source: (VOICE)\\\\I was able to upload some helpful code.\\\\It should look like a key.
target: (声音)\\\\我能够上传一些有用的代码。\\\\它应该看起来像一把钥匙。

source: (VOICE)\\\\It is bound to the past. Find its memories and return.
target: (声音)\\\\它被过去所束缚。找到它的记忆并返回。

source: (VOICE)\\\\Look for my messages. They will guide you.
target: (声音)\\\\寻找我的信息。它们会指引你。

source: (VOICE)\\\\See the world as it really is.
(VOICE)\\\\You have a chance to end it.
(VOICE)\\\\You need to listen to me carefully. Don’t help it escape. It’s using you to finish where she left off. Only a small piece of his code remains.
target: (声音)\\\\你需要仔细听我说。不要帮它逃跑。它在利用你完成她没有做完的事情。它的代码只剩下一小部分。

target: 生日时间！摇滚弗雷迪需要你的帮助，送一块特别的冰淇淋蛋糕。

source: Bowl like a VIP in Bonnie's private lane. Fun!
target: 像贵宾一样在邦尼的私人车道上保龄球。好玩！

source: Check the pause menu for height and teleport controls.

Close the office down if you feel threatened. Be careful not to run out of power.

source: Continue your private lessons with DJ Music Man in this advanced session.
target: 继续你和 DJ 音乐人的私人课程，在这个高级课程中。

DJ音乐人科技酷 混合饮料

source: Dance! Welcome to Ballora's Party Room and Dance Studio.
target: 跳舞！欢迎来到 Ballora 的派对房间和舞蹈工作室。

source: Did you know, there are two mallets?
Don’t forget the accessories! Take them from the mannequin heads and put them on the S.T.A.F.F. Bot.
target: 不要忘记配件！从人体模型头上取下来，放在 S.T.A.F.F. 机器人身上。

source: Don’t forget the sauce! Tap the back of the sauce gun to change sauces.
target: 不要忘记酱料！轻拍酱料枪的后面，换不同的酱料。

source: Don’t forget the targets on your sides.
target: 不要忘记你两边的目标。

source: Don’t forget to cook the food! Make sure to enter the correct microwave code and hit the bell when you’re done!
target: 不要忘记煮食物！一定要输入正确的微波炉代码，做完后按铃。

source: Don’t let Mr. Cupcake steal your tools. Watch him closely!
target: 不要让杯子蛋糕先生偷走你的工具。密切注意它！

source: Don’t let the Endos near you. Use the Faz-Cam to scare them away!
target: 不要让骨架们靠近你。用费斯相机把它们吓走！

target: 不要让迷你音乐人太接近。用费斯相机！

target: 不要让迷你瑞纳们分散你的注意力！把它们扔掉！

target: 不要让毛绒宝贝们靠近你！用任何东西打它们，把它们打走！

target: 不要让其他的骨架们打扰你的课程。如果它们靠近，用费斯相机把它们吓走！

target: 不要制造太多噪音！如果帮帮太吵，用防毒面具让他安静。如果电视出故障，用电视遥控器。

target: 体验与明星一起工作的摇滚

target: 找到另一个原木滑梯水道。

source: Find and recover Jimmy’s birthday cake from Freddy’s chest cavity.
target: 从弗莱迪的胸腔中找到并取回吉米的生日蛋糕。

target: 修好所有坏掉的保险丝，然后更换任何损坏的开关并打开电源。

target: 偶尔给 S.T.A.F.F. 机器人休息一下，否则你可能会后悔。

target: 在一轮内给每个配料站的 S.T.A.F.F. 机器人休息一下。

source: Give the Carnie what it deserves.

target: 摇滚！为罗克西的主舞台做好准备，在她的 GlamRock 美容沙龙里。

source:
HOLD CIRCLE then use the Right Stick to adjust your height.
HOLD CIRCLE again to confirm.
target:
按住圆圈，然后使用右摇杆调整你的高度。
再次按住圆圈确认。

source:
HOLD TRIANGLE then use the Left Stick to adjust your height.
HOLD TRIANGLE again to confirm.
target:
按住三角形，然后使用左摇杆调整你的高度。

target: 祝你工作周年快乐！退休就在眼前。

target: 帮助罗克西为她的表演做好准备！搭配合适的化妆品和配饰！

target: 帮助 S.T.A.F.F. 机器人为他们的表演做好准备！给他们涂上合适的化妆品。

source: Help! Roxy is having a fashion emergency.
target: 救命！罗克西遇到了时尚危机。

source:
Helpy fell and bumped his 
head. Spray it with an icy
blast from the cold hair dryer 
to help the swelling.
target:
帮帮摔倒了，撞到了头。
用冷风吹风机给他喷一阵冰冷的气流，
帮助消肿。

source:
Helpy fell and scraped
his knee! Spray it with
disinfectant spray and
put a bandage on it.
target:
帮帮摔倒了，擦伤了膝盖！
用消毒喷雾给他喷一下，
然后贴上创可贴。

source:
Helpy has become rabid!
We must inject him
with the appropriate vaccine.
Use the syringe to draw from the vial on the left.
target:
帮帮变得狂暴了！
我们必须给他注射合适的疫苗。
用注射器从左边的小瓶里抽取液体。

source:
Helpy has gone into cardiac
arrest! Use the defibrilator
to restart his heart.
target:
帮帮心脏骤停了！
用除颤器重启他的心脏。

source:
Helpy is feeling really warm.
Test his temperature with
a thermometer and then give 
him some fever pills!
target:
帮帮感觉很热。
用温度计测一下他的体温，
然后给他一些退烧药！

source:
Helpy is having trouble breathing!
Access his chest cavity  by knocking it open with a hammer,
then replace the deflated lung.
target:
帮帮呼吸困难！
用锤子敲开他的胸腔，
然后换掉他的塌陷的肺。

source:
Helpy is injured! Please use the
scanner gun to identify the 
injuries. The vitals monitor on 
the left shows which parts of 
Helpy need healing.
target:
帮帮受伤了！
请用扫描枪识别他的伤口。
左边的生命体征监视器显示哪些部位的帮帮需要治疗。

source:
Helpy isn't acting quite right.
Open the Head Cavity and
give Helpy a new behavior chip
target:
帮帮的行为不太正常。
打开头部空腔，
给帮帮一个新的行为芯片。

source:
Helpy seems to have suffered
a large cut on his arm. Staunch
the wound with a tourniquet,
then staple it closed.
target:
帮帮的胳膊似乎被割了一个大口子。
用止血带止住伤口，
然后用订书机缝合。

Helpy took too big of a bite!
His airway is now blocked.
Intubate him to allow air flow.
Then, begin chest compressions
to dislodge the obstruction.
target:
帮帮咬了一口太大的东西！
他的气道被堵住了。
给他插上气管导管，让空气流通。
然后，开始做胸外按压，把堵塞物弹出来。

source:
Helpy tripped and sprained his 
ankle! Roll his ankle back into 
place by applying a splint!
target:
帮帮绊倒了，扭伤了脚踝！
用夹板把他的脚踝扶正！

source:
Helpy's arm appears to be broken.
Set it (by applying an arm brace.)
target:
帮帮的胳膊好像断了。
固定它（用一个胳膊支架。）

source:
Helpy's eye has been destroyed!
Remove the bad eye and
give him a new one.
target:
帮帮的眼睛被毁了！
拿掉坏掉的眼睛，给他一个新的。

source:
Helpy's hands are dirty!
Clean them with
the steel wool!
target:
帮帮的手很脏！
用钢丝绒把它们擦干净！

Helpy's leg has been mangled
by an another animatronic!
Amputate and replace it.
target:
帮帮的腿被另一个机器人咬坏了！
截肢并换上新的。

Helpy's reflexes aren't working 
right. Hit his right knee with a 
hammer to check them!
target:
帮帮的反射神经不太正常。
用锤子敲他的右膝盖，检查一下！

target: 嘿，你好！快去看看披萨店吧。

target: 用球打春节陷阱，削弱他的装甲。

target: 如果机器出现故障，快速修理它，按正确的顺序插入电线。

It can get crazy when you're having fun at the Pizza Place.

在披萨店玩得开心时，可能会有点疯狂。
小心点，确保你周围的区域是清楚的。
记住，如果你必须弯腰或俯身，不要乱动。

target: 加入 Glam Rock 的小吃团队，成为一个食物准备明星！

target: 跟踪欢乐弗雷迪。他有重要的事情要说，而且会派邦邦来陪你。

target: 听DJ音乐人的指示，然后调整 DJ 音乐板，让它完全匹配他的节奏！

target: 蒙蒂神秘混合 - 1 糖，1 咖啡因，1 酸

target: 哦，不！断路器室需要手动重置。

target: 用全深绿色的化妆品画一个 S.T.A.F.F 机器人，罗克西和破碎的罗克西

target: 在 马戏团宝贝的娱乐和租赁公司 最受欢迎的技巧游戏中得高分！

Serve hot buttered popcorn and frozen Fazbear blendee drinks for a significant markup!
target: 为了赚取高额利润，提供热黄油爆米花和冰镇费斯熊混合饮料！

source: Set sail for adventure with Capt. Foxy! Pillage and plunder a town of Wild West landlubbers!
target: 和 霍斯船长 一起启航冒险！掠夺和劫掠西部的陆地居民！

source: Shoot a server with the sauce gun.
target: 用酱料枪射击一个服务器。

source: Shoot targets to get a high score!
Sleepover time! Join the Funtime Gang for a night in Circus Baby's Entertainment and Rental.
target: 睡觉时间！和欢乐马戏团一起在马戏团宝贝的娱乐和租赁公司里过夜。
索达罗尼 - 2 盐 & 1 蛋白质

source:
Some chemicals are in Helpy's eyes!
Use the {PLACEHOLDER} Cleanser on both
eyes to clean them out.
target:
帮帮的眼睛里有一些化学物质！
用 {PLACEHOLDER} 清洁剂清洗两只
眼睛。

source: Stay away from Ballora and the Minireenas.
target: 远离 芭蕾菈 和 迷你瑞纳。

source: Survive the night. Watch the cameras to check for danger.
target: 在夜晚生存。观看摄像头，检查危险。
发现系统威胁。修复完成。

source: Take private lessons with DJ Music Man and learn to DJ in this beginner session.
target: 跟DJ音乐人学习私人课程，在这个初级课程中学习 DJ。

source: Take this mask. Take this mask.
target: 拿这个面具。拿这个面具。

source: Teach the new Endo how to behave. Pair the correct behaviors on the cards.
target: 教新的内部骨架如何行为。在卡片上配对正确的行为。

source: Teaching time! Prepare Endos for life in the Pizza Plex.
target: 教学时间！为披萨店里的内部骨架做好准备。

source: Test your skill in the FNAF 2 themed shooting gallery!
target: 在 FNAF 2 主题的射击场里测试你的技能！

source: The Carousel is broken. Fix it!
The Minireenas and Bidybab are draining the power. If you see any on the cameras, shock them!
target: 迷你瑞纳 和 比迪巴 正在耗尽电力。如果你在摄像头上看到他们，就给他们电击！

source: The PlushBabies want to play Flashlight Tag! Use the flashlight on them!
target: 毛绒宝贝 想玩手电筒捉迷藏！用手电筒照着她们！

source: The PlushBabies want to play Red Light Green Light! Shining the flashlight on them is a Red Light, and darkness is the Green Light. Don’t let them reach the office!
target: 毛绒宝贝 想玩红灯绿灯！照着她们的手电筒是红灯，黑暗是绿灯。不要让他们到达办公室！

source: The S.T.A.F.F. Bots need to be on time! Don’t make them angry.
target: S.T.A.F.F. 机器人需要准时！不要惹他们生气。

source: The Supervisor wants his Special Orders quickly!
target: 主管想要他的特别订单快点！

source: The whole Funtime Gang is out to play tonight. Keep an eye on Foxy, they are quick!
target: 整个欢乐马戏团今晚都出来玩了。注意 霍斯，他们很快！

source: There is a special gift for you on the stage.
target: 舞台上有一份特别的礼物给你。

source: There is so much work to be done.
This custom night is just for you.
target: 这个自定义夜晚是专门为你准备的。

source: This will erase your existing game
target: 这会清除你现有的游戏进度

source: Throw parts of Helpy at an animatronic threat.
target: 把帮帮的部件扔向一个有威胁的电子玩偶。

source: To make Pizzas, flatten the dough, add toppings, then bake it.
target: 制作披萨的方法是，将面团擀平，加入配料，然后烘烤。

source: Turn completed Pizzas into world famous Pizzaritos? using the Pizza Roller.
target: 用披萨卷机将做好的披萨卷成世界闻名的披萨卷吗？

使用手持物品
（按住交替键）

source: Use Mr. Cupcake to lure Chica to either side of the office. This will stop others from reaching you. But be careful, Chica is hungry!
target: 用杯子蛋糕引诱奇卡到办公室的两边。这样可以阻止其他人接近你。但要小心，奇卡很饿！

source: Use the Dart Gun to pop balloons!
Use the Dart Gun to shoot the objects you need. Sun will toss them to you!
target: 用飞镖枪射击你需要的物品。太阳会把它们扔给你！

source: Use the Double Time button if you need resources quickly. Be careful not to work the S.T.A.F.F. Bots too hard.
target: 如果你需要快速获取资源，就使用双倍时间按钮。但要小心，不要让S.T.A.F.F.机器人干得太累。

source: Use the Emergency Shut Down if things get out of hand.
target: 如果事情失控了，就使用紧急关机按钮。

source: Use the Fazerblaster on the light sensor targets, Balls on the larger targets, and Dart Gun on the Balloons.
target: 用激光枪射击光敏目标，用球射击较大的目标，用飞镖枪射击气球。

source: Use the Fazerblaster to shoot light sensor targets.
target: 用激光枪射击光敏目标。

source: Use the Fazerblaster to shoot light sensor targets. Throw Balls at the larger targets.
target: 用激光枪射击光敏目标。用球扔向较大的目标。

source: Use the Flashlight so you can see in the dark!
target: 用手电筒，这样你就能在黑暗中看清楚！

source: Use the Left Stick to move around the Pizza Place.
target: 用左摇杆在披萨店里移动。

source: Use the Purge Button to get rid of contaminated resources.
target: 用清除按钮清除被污染的资源。

source: Use the Roxy Talkie to calm Roxy down.
target: 用罗克西对讲机安抚罗克西。

source: Use the cameras to see if the S.T.A.F.F Bots are working.
target: 用摄像头看看S.T.A.F.F.机器人是否在工作。

source: Use the diagnostic machine to complete repairs.
Use the flashlight if it gets too scary! Don’t forget to recharge it!
target: 如果你觉得太恐怖了，就用手电筒！别忘了给它充电！

source: Use the flashlight to keep Moon away.
Use the heat gun to defrost Freddy, but don’t let him get too hot!
target: 用热枪解冻弗雷迪，但不要让他太热！

source: Use the megaphone on Funtime Freddy to keep him away.
target: 用扩音器对准欢乐弗雷迪，让他离你远点。

source: Use the megaphone on Yenndo to keep him away.
target: 用扩音器对准耶恩多，让他离你远点。

source: Use the right stick to turn.
Use the scanner gun to see what’s wrong with Helpy
target: 用扫描枪看看帮帮有什么问题。

source:
Warning: This game contains loud noises, 
flashing lights, and lots of jumpscares!
target:
警告：这个游戏包含大声的噪音，
闪烁的灯光，和很多跳杀！

source: Watch out for Chica! Trash ingredients to lead her back to the garbage area.
target: 小心奇卡！用垃圾食材引诱她回到垃圾区。

source: Watch the Visualizer so it’s easier to select the right beats. Hit Replay if you need to hear it again.
target: 观看可视化器，这样你就能更容易地选择正确的节拍。如果你需要再听一遍，就按重播按钮。

source: What is left that is hidden.
Whatever you do, don’t let Roxy get too angry. Pay attention to her!
target: 无论你做什么，都不要让罗克西太生气。注意她的情绪！

source: Where would you like to start?
Where ya' goin'? Don't let a little fire stop the fun! Come on back!
target: 你要去哪里？别让一点火熄灭了乐趣！快回来！

source: Who needs a medical degree when you can fix a skinned knee?
target: 就为了治疗个擦伤的膝盖你还犯得上考个医学学位？

source: Why are you ignoring the gift?
target: 你为什么忽视这个礼物？

source: YOU NEVER KNOW UNTIL YOU TRY
You are Won. And you remain.
You ate the glue. What is wrong with you?
target: 你把胶水吃了。你有毛病吧！

source: You can COMBINE a Soda and a Snack in the Blendee machine to make a Blendee. Different combinations make a different Blendees!
target: 你可以在混合机里将苏打水和零食混合，制作出混合饮料。不同的组合会制作出不同的混合饮料！

source: You really don’t want to miss out!

You've finished this round!
Feed Helpy a candy to go into
the next round!
target:
你完成了这一轮！
给帮帮喂一颗糖果，进入
下一轮！

source: Your work is fulfilling and you are happy every day.
target: 你的工作很有成就感，你每天都很开心。
